## 6. How to Use This Document

Feed this entire upgraded document to Gemini with a prompt like:

> "I have just completed a massive Phase 1-4 structural V3 overhaul of my portfolio website. Based on this new walkthrough outlining the current state of my WebGL Three.js node cluster, IntersectionObserver SVG data pipelines, Quake-style Dev Terminal, and custom vanilla SVG sparklines for GitHub telemetry, generate a new comprehensive prompt for Gemini 3.1 Pro. The new prompt should focus on the NEXT LEVEL of iteration—e.g., integrating an AI backend to make the Dev Terminal fully conversational, migrating the application to an SSR edge-compute framework for SEO mastery, or orchestrating complex 3D shader manipulation."
